<item>
            <title>[LU-6968] Update the whole header in llog_cancel_rec()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6968</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In llog_cancel_rec(), it will update the whole header to clear the bit of the record, and for update log, it will write 32k byte for canceling each record. So we need fix this as adding record, only updating parts of header, instead of the whole header.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
